Genderize
=========

Genderize modifies existing I18n.translate method so it can provide gender-based distinctions.


Example
=======

fr:
  test1: "affamé[[e]]"
  test2: "amat[[eur,rice]]"

I18.t :test1, :gender => :male # "affamé"
I18.t :test1, :gender => :female # "affamée"
I18.t :test2, :gender => :male # "amateur"
I18.t :test2, :gender => :female # "amatrice
